window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A BIRTHDAY HEX</b><br> <br> Charm has reached her eighteenth birthday. What she doesn’t know is that something insidious has waited all her life for this moment. When a surprise gift is given to her, she must make a decision that will change her life forever.<br> <br> <b>ENRAPTURED</b><br> <br> Auryn has a wicked secret. She relishes watching the sirens of the sea bring villagers to their agonizing deaths. Until, on one fateful night, Auryn is faced with something that could grant her all of her heart’s desires. If she is willing to pay the price.</p>"; 
